ook shows that he supplies tools for thinking that are as valuable today as they were in the nineteenth century.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 7aPHILOSOPHY / Movements / Utilitarianism.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertColumbia University Press Complete eBook-Package 2023z978311074967040uhttps://doi.org/10.7312/kitc2041440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780231555395423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780231555395/original  a978-3-11-074967-0  Columbia University Press Complete eBook-Package 2023b2023  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK